HEADWORD: Empark
<hw>Em*park"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>em-</ets> + <ets>park</ets>: cf. OF. <ets>emparchier</ets>,
<ets>emparkier</ets>. Cf. <er>Impark</er>.]</ety> <def>To make a park
of; to inclose, as with a fence; to impark.</def>
